            <p><choice><sic><supplied reason="lost">Μ</supplied>νημῖον</sic><corr>μνημεῖον</corr></choice> Σαμάκωνος ἀ<lb break="no"/><unclear>ρ</unclear>χιδιακόνου <choice><reg>ἀπογενομένου</reg><orig>ἀπογενόμενος</orig></choice>
               <lb/>
               <choice><sic>Μνημῖον</sic><corr>μνημεῖον</corr></choice> Σαμά<lb break="no"/>κωνος Ζάβδα<lb/> ἀρχιδιακόνου<lb/> ἀπογενόμενος<lb/>
               ἐτῶν <num>μʹ</num> ἐν τῷ<lb/>
               <choice><sic>εισζμῷ</sic><corr>σεισμῷ</corr></choice>
               <expan><abbr>ἔτ</abbr><ex>ους</ex></expan>
               <num>μνηʹ</num><lb/>
               <choice><sic>μηνὶ</sic><corr>μηνὸς</corr></choice> Ἀρτεμισίου<lb/>
               <num>ηκʹ</num>
               <choice><sic>θάρσι</sic><corr>θάρσει</corr></choice>
               <choice><sic>οὐδὶ<lb break="no"/>ς</sic><corr>οὐδείς</corr></choice> ἀθάνατος<lb/>
               <expan><abbr>ἡμ</abbr><ex>έ</ex><abbr>ρ</abbr><ex>ᾳ</ex></expan> Σελήνης</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0024.translation" corresp="#zoor0024.transcription">
            <p>Monument of Samakon, (the) archdeacon, who died... Monument of Samakon, (son) of
                    Zabdas, (the) archdeacon, who died (at the age) of 40 years during the
                    earthquake, in (the) year 258, on (the) 28th (day) of (the) month Artemisios. Be
                    of good cheer, no one (is) immortal. (He died) on the day of (the) Moon
                    (Monday).</p>
         </div>
      <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p><w xml:id="zoor0024-1" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic><supplied reason="lost">Μ</supplied>νημῖον</sic><corr>μνημεῖον</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-2" xml:lang="grc">Σαμάκωνος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-3" xml:lang="grc">ἀ<unclear>ρ</unclear>χιδιακόνου</w> <orig xml:id="zoor0024-4" xml:lang="grc">ἀπογενόμενος</orig> <w xml:id="zoor0024-5" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>Μνημῖον</sic><corr>μνημεῖον</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-6" xml:lang="grc">Σαμάκωνος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-7" xml:lang="grc">Ζάβδα</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-8" xml:lang="grc">ἀρχιδιακόνου</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-9" xml:lang="grc">ἀπογενόμενος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-10" xml:lang="grc">ἐτῶν</w> <num xml:id="zoor0024-11" xml:lang="grc">μʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0024-12" xml:lang="grc">ἐν</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-13" xml:lang="grc">τῷ</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-14" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>εισζμῷ</sic><corr>σεισμῷ</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-15" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>ἔτ</abbr><ex>ους</ex></expan></w> <num xml:id="zoor0024-16" xml:lang="grc">μνηʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0024-17" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>μηνὶ</sic><corr>μηνὸς</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-18" xml:lang="grc">Ἀρτεμισίου</w> <num xml:id="zoor0024-19" xml:lang="grc">ηκʹ</num> <w xml:id="zoor0024-20" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>θάρσι</sic><corr>θάρσει</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-21" xml:lang="grc"><choice><sic>οὐδὶς</sic><corr>οὐδείς</corr></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-22" xml:lang="grc">ἀθάνατος</w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-23" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>ἡμ</abbr><ex>έ</ex><abbr>ρ</abbr><ex>ᾳ</ex></expan></w> <w xml:id="zoor0024-24" xml:lang="grc">Σελήνης</w></p>
</div>
